➜全网首发！这家距离魔都1.5H的神秘酒庄目测要火
http://www.sohu.com/a/411199938_380622	20799
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200803/6af2db7f15a24490adc73dff83721554.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>距魔都1.5H</strong>的缥缈山间，</p>
<p>诞生一处<strong>全新精品酒庄</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200803/9a231c1e2f014720a2d96ed5d25aeab8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>耗时多年，精心打造，</p>
<p><strong>360度环绕式建筑</strong>傲立山间，</p>
<p>坐拥约<strong>600亩葡萄庄园。</strong></p>
<p>亦是<strong>中国配套超好的精品酒庄，</strong></p>
<p>设有47间<strong>现代风格客房，</strong></p>
<p>并引入<strong>米其林二星餐饮品牌。</strong></p>
<p><strong>全网首发</strong>，来一探究竟！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200803/600b2d33412c43bd870f5cb305c7866f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
