<p><strong>虹桥南丰城</strong></p>
<p><strong>2020夏日祭热力来袭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200803/58bf82ee08994b77ab171a32f269fc72.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
